data.description: Experience country living while being in close driving distance to both Abingdon and Bristol! This mobile home sits on a beautiful piece of 2.02 acre property! Sellers state that the view of the sunset over the mountains is their favorite thing about this property along with the deer and birds they see regularly from their back porch. Enter in the front door and you will find an open concept living room and eat-in kitchen. Right off the kitchen is a good sized pantry and a laundry room. The master suite with walk-in closet is located on one side of the home to allow for privacy. The other two bedrooms and guest bath is located at the opposite end. Carpet throughout the property with tile in the kitchen, laundry room, and bathrooms. Information deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Buyer or buyers agent to verify all information.
